    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>diced chorizo</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped thyme</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the pan and mix well</p>",
